About Me

Hello! My name is Manisha Nallakatla and I am a Computer Science major and Data Science minor at the University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill.

When I was younger, I really enjoyed drawing, making short films, braiding hair, and pretty much anything else that required me to be creative. One of my favorite movies growing up was Iron Man, and I was enamored by the idea of honing my creative skills to create something with technology! Thus, my love for coding was born...
